{"tid":1723592,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實公司膠層對員工性命安危尤如垃圾 咁都唔自發罷工？","createTime":"2019-11-15T08:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T16:15:29.000Z","uid":339822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8d5d1c9f80185aa445622b44bd1a138758de1896","tid":1723592,"uid":339822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:37:16.000Z","msg":"新手代友開post<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;MxM M字頭冷血女高層不理同事生死，淨係識問幾時做到生意，唔放催淚彈唔開槍唔放火就唔放人走，同事返工用幾多時間安唔安全唔會問，放工有無車返屋企唔會問，只係問點解無生意，喂大佬! 你試吓行出去是但一個mall睇吓，點樣做到生意呀？同事生命賤過地底泥&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n我知道唔止零售業 好多行業都有呢啲情況<br />\n但其實各位和理非 你做緊間公司係咁仆街嘅話<br />\n仲值唔值得你拎條命同佢搏？<br />\n先唔講催淚彈二噁英<br />\n宜家成條街隨時有失控黑警暴徒<br />\n人生安全嚴重受威脅<br />\n其實大家應該自發罷工 (原因: 無車好危險唔舒服)<br />\n而唔係要班前線為大家擋完子彈 俾狗行私刑 被自殺 強姦<br />\n然後大家好嬲 覺得好慘 然後又繼續去返工<br />\n好似我朋友咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家都肯行多一步<br />\n三罷會更成功<br />\nSorry for 1999<br />\n<br />\n#前線員工都係人<br />\n#唔好當前線係搵錢機器<br />\n#無前線幫公司做生意幾高嘅膠層都係多9餘<br />\n#光復香港 時代革命<br />\n#成立獨立調查委員會"},{"pid":"2d8e591d6ca07623a5f76fa2f0c74cd4f2c3d72c","tid":1723592,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:37:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組會keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYe6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=1961334a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務<br />\n<br />\nSenator Scott 幫香港人出聲<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Rt + like </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senrickscott/status/1195147582609252353?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenrickscott%2Fstatus%2F1195147582609252353%3Fs%3D21&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYe6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=880acacb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenrickscott%2Fstatus%2F1195147582609252353%3Fs%3D21&h=37d03fec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senrickscott/status/1195147582609252353?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"d717ecaab6c71dbb83a31187a780d92c8155d82b","tid":1723592,"uid":9648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:58:03.000Z","msg":"呢啲無視員工安危嘅公司要抵制啦<br />\n<br />\nMXM得支西會用，而家佢哋都怕死唔黎買啦，開門黎把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21935c0d142c442f3be8b5247206cbf45d99a6c","tid":1723592,"uid":9648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:26:24.000Z","msg":"話說琴晚向sales界朋友問起sales界安危情況，佢睇完個post話佢識人响喺MCM 做！求證之後個回應係嗰間嘢唔理員工死活係事實！<br />\n<br />\n以下為該員工原文：<br />\n<br />\n「呢啲公司真係把撚，出面封晒路都覺得仲有生意？到走嘅時候已經無車，一個唔好彩中催淚，俾狗咬係咪公司負責？<br />\n<br />\n罷工咁多日都無安排，總之就繼續返工開門搵錢，其他牌子一早就延遲開門，一係就直頭唔開保員工安全<br />\n<br />\n成班同事仲要日日排除萬難返工，完全冇當過大家係人，咁嘅時勢，仲邊會有人買嘢嫁，仲要冒住生命危險黎買係MCM？呢啲女膠層淨係掛住做支那人生意當員工係condom，真係要集體罷工」<br />\n<br />\n#幫佢做下宣傳<br />\n#全民三罷<br />\n#光復香港"},{"pid":"e65eb834766d7f338df8c8ba1820c0e006b869b6","tid":1723592,"uid":9648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:27:35.000Z","msg":"幫慘情打工仔自推十連<br />\n<br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"98127635292f9887d2544df1ba538c0d7e64c135","tid":1723592,"uid":9648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:27:47.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"237c71124c00b4a2469ca1b299a83e1b8f8780bf","tid":1723592,"uid":9648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:28:01.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"2fcd593b4480aab97065ac6556be3e80bdad3e50","tid":1723592,"uid":9648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:28:21.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"23868bf5eebab6569c13e293e6fc